{"tid":1736502,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"1119 大風向","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:18:19.000Z","uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cba0a9078814524ed7b4d70f3169627407616a1","tid":1736502,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"一入夜就 feel 到返風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心身體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ykh9y4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkh9y4K.png&h=384b63be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與冷鋒相關的強烈東北季候風正為華南帶來清涼的天氣。<br />\n<br />\n在上午二時，強烈熱帶風暴海鷗集結在馬尼拉之東北偏北約520公里，預料向西移動，時速約10公里，移向呂宋海峽一帶。<br />\n<br />\n本港地區今日天氣預測<br />\n<br />\n大致天晴及乾燥。早上天氣清涼，<span style=\"color: red;\">市區最低氣溫約17度</span>，新界再低兩、三度。日間最高氣溫約23度。吹和緩至清勁偏北風，離岸間中吹強風。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f524eb2d55a11a3767e112bba029fbda4a44e362","tid":1736502,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"好凍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be16afd44040748da01a3a491b8d5d01daa92918","tid":1736502,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddb73d1c627b1619ef698b2a04446d3b3fc90a0","tid":1736502,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:12:34.000Z","msg":"今日唯一得着係好多和理非都升左lv"},{"pid":"2479da1356515207db8388508bbef4e653ec0e3f","tid":1736502,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f524eb2d55a11a3767e112bba029fbda4a44e362","tid":1736502,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"好凍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma